ngredient formula supports your nutritional intake during periods when dietary sources may be insufficient. It is designed to support general health and wellbeing and maintain vitamin C, zinc and magnesium levels in the body when dietary intake is inadequate. Whether you&#x27;re looking to complement your diet or support your daily wellness routine, it’s a simple choice for everyday health. Good health changes everything—nourish your day with Blackmores ZinvitC250. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Immune System Health General Health No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Combines the benefits of vitamin C and zinc in one convenient supplement. Supports healthy immune function. Maintains zinc and vitamin C levels in the body. Maintains general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 1-2 tablets a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding please talk with your health professional before use. WARNING: Contains zinc, which may be dangerous if taken in large amounts or for a long period. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Combines the benefits of vitamin C and zinc in one convenient supplement. Supports healthy immune function. Maintains zinc and vitamin C levels in the body. Maintains general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 1-2 tablets a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeedi