lled probiotic strains to help maintain vaginal health and support vaginal healthy flora/microflora. It also helps maintain general health and wellbeing. This convenient, shelf-stable formula is travel friendly and requires no refrigeration. Designed specifically for women, it supports healthy vaginal flora - where and when you need it. Good health changes everything. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Vaginal Health No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy No Added Soya Bean Benefits & How To Use Benefits Contains clinically trialled* strains based on scientific evidence. 2.3 billion good bacteria per capsule. Helps support good vaginal bacteria levels. Maintains vaginal health. Gluten free. Comes in a handbag friendly canister pack. Travel friendly, no refrigeration required. *Reid et al, FEMS immunol med microbiol 2003 35(2): 131-4 Dosage Adults Take 1 capsule once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during first 3 months of pregnancy. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Benefits Dosage Warnings Contains clinically trialled* strains based on scientific evidence. 2.3 billion good bacteria per capsule. Helps support good vaginal bacteria levels. Maintains vaginal health. Gluten free. Comes in a handbag friendly canister pack. Travel friendly, no refrigeration required. *Reid et al, FEMS immunol med microbiol 2003 35(2): 131-4 Adults Take 1 capsule once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during first 3 months of pregnancy. If you have any pre-existing conditions, 