Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Concentrated Curcumin + Active Support Size Size 120 tablets Blackmores Concentrated Curcumin + Active Support combines TurmXTRA™, magnesium, and vitamins C and D in a convenient one-a-day formula. It helps maintain joint health, supports muscle function, and promotes collagen formation. This formulation also helps support general health and wellbeing and aids the absorption of dietary vitamins and minerals. Designed to be taken daily with food, it’s ideal for individuals wanting to maintain physical activity and nutritional support throughout the day. Good health changes everything. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Inflammation Muscle Health Mild Joint Pain Joint Health No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits A triple-action formula for maintaining joint, bone & muscle health. Magnesium for muscle health, Curcumin for anti-inflammatory action, Vitamin D to maintain bone health and Vitamin C to support immune system health. May relieve pain after exercise. Maintains joint cartilage and collagen health. Supports general health and wellbeing. Antioxidant action to reduce free radicals formed in the body. Contains bioavailable TurmXTRA® 60N curcumin formulated for optimal absorption. Dosage Adults Take 2 tablets once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Do not use if you have pre-existing liver conditions. In very rare cases, Curcuma species may harm the liver. Stop use and see a doctor if you have yellowing skin/eyes or unusual: fatigue, nausea, appetite loss, abdominal pain, dark urine or itching. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings A triple-action formula for maintaining joint, bone & muscle health. Magnesium for muscle health, Curcumin for anti-inflammatory action, Vitamin D to maintain bone health and Vitamin C to support immune system health. May relieve pain after exercise. Maintains joint cartilage and collagen health. Supports general health and wellbeing. Antioxidant action to reduce free radicals formed in the body. Contains bioavailable TurmXTRA® 60N curcumin formulated for optimal absorption. Adults Take 2 tablets once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Do not use if you have pre-existing liver conditions. In very rare cases, Curcuma species may harm the liver. Stop use and see a doctor if you have yellowing skin/eyes or unusual: fatigue, nausea, appetite loss, abdominal pain, dark urine or itching. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with y